# MotherDuck: Cloud SQL Analytics Without the Overhead

**The serverless DuckDB data warehouse that scales to terabytes—for data teams and customer-facing analytics.**

---

## What is MotherDuck?

MotherDuck is a cloud analytics platform powered by DuckDB that delivers fast, cost-efficient SQL analytics without infrastructure overhead. It combines the performance of local compute with cloud scale, enabling both internal BI workloads and customer-facing analytics at millisecond latency.

---

## Key Features

### Dual Execution Query Engine
Run queries locally, in the cloud, or hybrid across both. MotherDuck's query planner automatically routes execution where it completes fastest—repurposing your laptop's unused compute for local analytics while leveraging cloud resources when you need scale.

### Per-User Tenancy (Ducklings)
Each user gets their own dedicated DuckDB instance ("Duckling"), eliminating resource contention. No more waiting for queries because another user is consuming too much compute. Choose from five instance sizes: Pulse, Standard, Jumbo, Mega, and Giga.

### User-Level Cost Visibility
Built-in CPU visibility at the user level enables accurate cost attribution and proactive optimization. Predict costs before they spike—no surprise bills when usage scales.

### Read Scaling
Provision dedicated read replicas for BI tools, sized to match your workload requirements. Handle thousands to millions of concurrent queries for customer-facing analytics.

### Universal Data Format Support
Query data where it lives: Parquet, JSON, CSV, Iceberg, Excel, and plaintext. Connect directly to S3-compatible object storage, Postgres, Salesforce, Stripe, and more.

---

## Use Cases

### Data Warehousing
Consolidate scattered data for internal BI and analytics. Build pure SQL pipelines, share data across teams, and go from question to insight without infrastructure friction.

### Customer-Facing Analytics
Embed analytics directly into your product with near real-time, low-latency insights. MotherDuck's architecture—from per-user tenancy to Wasm support—handles the unique requirements of user-facing analytics at scale.

---

## Modern Duck Stack Ecosystem

MotherDuck integrates with 40+ tools across the data stack:

- **Ingestion:** Fivetran, Airbyte, Estuary, dlt
- **Transformation:** dbt, SQLMesh, Tobiko
- **BI & Visualization:** Tableau, Power BI, Omni, Metabase
- **Data Science:** Hex, Jupyter, Google Colab, Marimo
- **Orchestration:** Airflow, Dagster, Prefect, Kestra
- **Data Quality:** Monte Carlo, Secoda, Soda, Great Expectations

---

## Why Technical Leaders Choose MotherDuck

> "MotherDuck with DuckDB was by far the fastest of the OLAP platforms we evaluated—both in the cloud and run on our developer's machines—bridging price and performance and greatly increasing productivity."
> — **Jim O'Neill**, CTO and Co-founder, FinQore

> "MotherDuck is insanely performant, and there's no infrastructure to manage. The cost of experimentation is incredibly low—which means we can afford to ask more questions and build more features, faster."
> — **Kristov Paulus**, Founder & CIO, Kultura Capital

> "Moving to MotherDuck, a billed-by-the-second cloud offering, is a no-brainer for us, considering the elegance and efficiency of a single node system compared to traditional OLAP solutions."
> — **Nico Ritschel**, Director of Engineering, atm.com

---

## Get Started

MotherDuck offers a generous free tier for experimentation. Try it for 21 days free—no credit card required.

[Start Free →](https://app.motherduck.com/?auth_flow=signup)

[Book a Demo →](https://motherduck.com/contact-us/product-expert/)
